<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Pepsiman is a 3d action game that takes place over four stages splits in three sections.
                  <br><br>Story:
                  <br>A hand is seen opening a refrigerator and it took 5 pepsi cans. The camera changes to a man holding some snacks and 5 pepsi cans is seen walking out of the store."Hey,let's start the game!"he says.
                  <br><br>Pepsiman is seen running away from the camera. He meets a man wearing a Pepsi T-shirt in front of a Pepsi truck. He is the driver of the truck and says: "Ah Pepsiman,you got here just in the perfect time. I've got a call from from the Bedding machine; it ran out of Pepsi! And I'm just on my way there but I got a flat tyre. There are a bunch of people in front of the Bedding machine; they want Pepsi! And the word is it they just started a riot! I'll find a garage over there, as soon as I get to Display ,but it looks like it's gonna take some time. Can you do something, Pepsiman?"So Pepsiman rushes to action.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>CM Pepsiman familiar with the main character, such exhilaration run run run and run the 3D action across the United States. Sense of speed, of action, humor combine the three, but still very active in the world Pepsiman CM. Pepsi to deliver the world's people lack Pepsi,'ll continue working with all 16 stages Pepsiman.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>3D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Fantasy theme.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

